{
  "texts": [
    "The decision time is almost linear depending on the number of stations.",
    "The WIP also indicates a strong influence on the decision time.",
    "The restriction and transport speed parameters indicate no significant impact on the decision time.",
    "The makespan is a scalar to measure the performance of the control algorithm in LMAS.",
    "Thus, the makespan of the trained MARL algorithm is compared with a random agent and the untrained MARL algorithm."
  ]
}